# NAME

hnefatafl-ai - Hnefatafl Copenhagen AI

# SYNOPSIS

hnefatafl-ai \[OPTIONS\]

# DESCRIPTION

This is an AI client that connects to a server.

# OPTIONS

: *\-\-username* _USERNAME_


: *\-\-password* _PASSWORD_

    [default: ]

: *\-\-role* _ROLE_

    attacker or defender

: *\-\-host* _HOST_

    connect to the HTP server at host
    [default: hnefatafl.org]

: *\-\-ai* _AI_

    choose an AI to play as
    [default: banal]

:  *\-\-challenger* _CHALLENGER_

    challenge the AI with AI CHALLENGER


: *-h*, *\-\-help*

    print help (see a summary with '-h')

: *-V*, *\-\-version*

    print version

